# Everything you should know about this pack:

1. This pack comes with a help function to tell players what to do
	`/trigger ts_help`

TO CREATE:
2. Place a armour stand in location of 1x1 detection area
3. Run function "/function ts:create_thunder_shrine" within 3 blocks of any armour stand
4. The nearest armour stand within 3 blocks will be the location of the new shrine

TO REMOVE:
5. To delete a shrine, stand within 3 blocks of it and run `/function ts:remove_thunder_shrine`

NOTE:
6. If you Ctrl+Throw a stack of nether stars into the shrine, nothing will happen.
					ONLY 1 NETHER STAR IS ACCEPTED!
